						               													<description>English description:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Colmeia - Micro-game (The Beehive - Micro-game) is a game reimplementation of A Colmeia.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this game, players will have to leave with his bee his hive, and take 3 nectar the game board, and return to their hive. The first player to do this will be the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To move your bee, use tiles of arrows that will make your bee walk through the board. There is also, at the end of your turn, choose 1 tile (Green, Yellow or Red) and put these Tiles in Tray. These Tiles, change the tempo of the game, adding new barriers and also giving some advantages to bees. You can also earn Nectar + 1, more trees or problems with pesticides.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Portuguese description:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Colmeia - Micro-jogo &amp;eacute; uma reimplementa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do jogo A Colmeia.&amp;#10;Neste jogo, os jogadores ter&amp;atilde;o que sair com sua abelha de sua colmeia, e pegar 3 n&amp;eacute;ctares pelo tabuleiro do jogo, e voltar para sua colmeia. O primeiro jogador que fizer isso, ser&amp;aacute; o vencedor.&amp;#10;Para mover sua abelha, utilizar&amp;aacute; tiles de setas que far&amp;aacute; com que sua abelha ande pelo tabuleiro. Ter&amp;aacute; tamb&amp;eacute;m, no final de seu turno, que escolher 1 tile (Verde, Amarelo ou Vermelho) e colocar estes Tiles no Tabuleiro. Estes Tiles, alteram o andamento do jogo, acrescentando novas barreiras e tamb&amp;eacute;m dando algumas vantagens para as abelhas. Poder&amp;aacute; tamb&amp;eacute;m ganhar + 1 Nectar, mais &amp;aacute;rvores ou surgirem problemas com agrot&amp;oacute;xicos.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
